<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Bootstrap 5 Website Example</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</head>
<style>
nav {
    height: 50px;
    background-color: black;
    color: white;
}
nav a {
    color: white;
    font-size: 30px;
}
body p {
    max-height: 190px;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
}
.Subsection {
    border: 2px solid black;
    border-radius: 5px;
}
.ProjectBox {
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid blue;
    border-radius: 5px;
    float: left;
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
}
.ProjectButton {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 5px;
    left: 5px;
}
.dropdown {
  display: inline-block;
  position: relative;
}
.dropdown-content {
  display: none;
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  background-color: white;
  overflow: auto;
  box-shadow: 0px 10px 10px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}
.dropdown:hover .dropdown-content {
  display: block;
}
.dropdown-content a {
    font-size: 15px;
  display: block;
  color: #000000;
  padding: 5px;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.dropdown-content a:hover {
  color: #FFFFFF;
  background-color: #00A4BD;
}
</style>

<nav>
    <a href="/projects">Home</a>
    <div class="dropdown">
    <button>Account</button>
    <div class="dropdown-content">
        <a href="/dummyval">Sign In</a>
        <a href="/notyetimplimented">Sign Up</a>
    </div>
    </div>
</nav>


<body>

<!-- Header and introduction -->
<h1>Sean Lord's Portfolio</h1>
<p>This is the portfolio of Sean Lord, UCCS graduate with a 
<a href="https://physics.uccs.edu/bs-in-physics">Bachelor of Science in Physics</a>, 4 years of professional coding experience, and is currently working towards a 
<a href="https://eas.uccs.edu/cs/academics/undergraduate-programs/bachelor-of-science-in-computer-science">Bachelor in Computer Science</a>, also from UCCS.
</p>

<div class="Subsection">
    <p>Programming languages</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Java</li>
        <li>Python</li>
        <li>C</li>
        <li>Ruby</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="Subsection">
    <p>Tertiary skills</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Microsoft suite familiarity(Word, Excel, Powerpoint)</li>
        <li>Public speaking skills</li>
        <li>Communication skills</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div id="projects">
  <% @projects.each do |project| %>
    <div class="ProjectBox">
    <h3><%= project.title %></h3>
    <p>
        <%= project.description %>
    </p>
    <form class="ProjectButton" action="<%= project_path(project) %>">
        <input  type="submit" value="See this project" />
    </form>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>

</body>
</html>